CHAPTER I
PRELIMINARY
Short title and commencement.
1.(1) These regulations may be called the Securities and Exchange Board of India (Portfolio Managers) Regulations, 2020.
(2) These regulations shall come into force on the date of their publication in the Official Gazette.
