(2)The report referred to in sub-regulation (1) may be made available on the website of the portfolio manager with restricted access to each client.
(3)On termination of the contract, the portfolio manager shall give a detailed statement of accounts to the client and settle the account with the client as agreed in the contract.
(4)The client shall have the right to obtain details of his portfolio from the portfolio managers.
