33.The Board may ask portfolio manager to disclose any information as and when required including the following: -
(a)particulars regarding the management of a portfolio;
(b)any change in the information or particulars previously furnished, which have a bearing on the certificate granted to him;
(c)the names of the clients whose portfolio it has managed;
